DoomGeneric vendored source
Upstream: https://github.com/ozkl/doomgeneric
Commit: dcb7a8dbc7a16ce3dda29382ac9aae9d77d21284
License: GPL-2.0-only (see LICENSE)

HuesOS compiles this as the separate `huesos-doom` userspace program. It is
not linked into the MIT kernel or native Rust libraries. Platform integration
and the purpose-built compatibility libc live under
`crates/huesos-userspace/doom/`.
